title: Amana Side by Side Refrigerator ASI2275FRSS
description:
In this video we take a closer look at the Amana refrigerator model ASI2275FRSS.  For more details or to place an order please visit us at Abt.com: http://www.abt.com/product/107206/Amana-Stainless-Steel-Side-By-Side-Refrigerator-ASI2275FRS.html

- Capacity
